arts.ttl: Feyenoord up to third with win over Groningen
arts.sum: Feyenoord have risen to third in the Eredivisie with a 4-1 win over Groningen on Wednesday. After only ten minutes, Feyenoord had the lead with Anis Hadj Moussa finding the bottom corner. Just after the half hour mark, Igor Paixao doubled the lead with a fierce strike.
